title: BREAKING: Storm Doris sparks huge fire on train line as power cables crash down in gales
text:
BREAKING: Storm Doris sparks huge fire on train line as power cables crash down in gales BREAKING: Storm Doris sparks huge fire on train line as power cables crash down in gales A FIRE at Ware station has engulfed the line in flames after Storm Doris brought power cables onto the track. PUBLISHED: 13:56, Thu, Feb 23, 2017 | UPDATED: 14:06, Thu, Feb 23, 2017 @camera_markitv Burning trees fell onto tracks in Ware 
Emergency services rushed to Ware in Hertfordshire as bushes were blown onto power lines and caught on fire. 
The burning debris landed on the track - halting services to and from the station. 
More follows... Devastation as Storm Doris leaves ONE dead Thu, February 23, 2017
